<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ạ̹lhy lạ rjạʾ ly swạk tạq qlby tạq lby ạ̉n ạ̉fwz brḍạk
 ạlqrạr- mlʾ rwḥk ạ̉sẖtyạqy hbh ly wạstr kẖṭạy
 yrtwy mnh gẖlyly fyk lạ gẖyr rjạy
 2- ạ̉nt rby nwr qlby ạ̉nt ḥṣn ạ̉tqyạk
 fạmlạ̉n yạrb qlby rwḥ qds mn ʿlạk
 3-qlby ạmlạ̉ rwḥ ḥb rwḥ br wslạm
 rwḥ ạymạn wṣbr rwḥ lṭf wwỷạm
 4-mlʾ rwḥk ḥyạty mlʾ rwḥk ạlwdyʿ
 mlʾ rwḥk ạ̉mnḥny yạ yswʿ yạ smyʿ</lyrics>
<title>yạ ạ̹lhy</title>
